ID: 11054
Title: email account
Syntax Type: type
Addon: SkMail
Syntax Pattern:
emailaccount
Description:
Representing of Email configuration/account
```applescript
    set {_email} to configured email account "example"
    send address of {_email}
    send type of {_email}
    send host of {_email}
    send port of {_email}
    send auth of {_email}
    send starttls of {_email}
    send service of {_email}
```
Compatible Addon Version: 1.0
Addon Link: https://github.com/cooffeeRequired/SkriptMail/releases
